	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I post in this forum cos i think is a hardware releated thing.
<br />Why the NES cant make a "ppu mem access on request" and we have to read twice 0x2007 to get the correct value? i mean electronically how this happens?

		

