	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Using the PPU to access VRAM is usually more efficient than if it were accessed directly by the CPU, due to the auto incrementing (especially the 32-byte increment mode).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


